# Persistent Agent Rules (CLI Agents)

1. Follow schema-first development: define/modify contracts before implementation code.
2. Maintain strict package boundaries between platform core and domain plugins.
3. For Dataverse integration, implement adapter seams in integration modules; avoid hardcoding endpoints.
4. Require typed interfaces, explicit error envelopes, and input validation on all service boundaries.
5. Keep migration notes in milestone documents when data contracts change.
